edu.umn.biomedicus.common.dictionary

Interface BidirectionalDictionary

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBidirectionalDictionary, StandardBidirectionalDictionary

    public BidirectionalDictionary

    A collection of term (string) to integer mappings in both directions.
